  "body": "Because recovery go-routines are interrupted in the middle of their jobs, they do not write anything into the `out` channel, and the main loop gets stuck trying to read from that channel.\r\nTwo possible solution - let recovery goroutines finish their jobs before interrupting them, or make the main loop interruptible in the middle",
